name: Mushroom queen 'Rebeth'
description:
Mushroom queen 'Rebeth' was Born from the Spores of Fungi & Mushrooms, She then grew large enough to gain the titles 'The Goddess Mushroom' and more Recently, 'Turned Mushroom' For she has Locked herself up for a Millennium, Inhaling the Fumes that the child Spores that lay upon her Body Caused her to turn Demon-like, Which the People now fear.
